                "body": "<img src=\"https://static.remotasks.com/uploads/6892e922522126f1742d8678/1754586498798_fsdqic.png\" alt=\"Step 1: Write and Understand the Prompt  Before writing your prompt, confirm the correct task setup by reviewing three key items in the task header. First, your prompt category must follow the required prompt type exactly. Second, your image category must match the specified image type for the task. Third, you must follow the assigned image count for all prompts, which will be either Single or Multi-Image.  If the image count is labeled Single, you may only upload one image, even if the conversation has multiple turns. If the count is Multi-Image, then you should upload more than one image. STEM or coding-related prompts are not allowed unless your assigned category specifically permits them.  These rules must be followed for the first turn in the task. Later turns may vary in prompt category, image type, or image count.\">"
