              "type": "rich_text",
              "contents": {
                "singleSelect": true,
                "body": "<img src=\"https://static.remotasks.com/uploads/6892e922522126f1742d8678/1754469289556_pgxip1.png\" alt=\"The ideal response: Left Box:  An ideal response typically  Fully follows the instructions in the prompt  Demonstrates deep understanding of the task’s purpose and goals  Addresses every part of the prompt clearly and completely  Maintains appropriate tone, language, and formatting  Shows no major flaws in truthfulness, coherence, or writing quality  Right Side:  Use this as your north star:  Every rubric criterion should help distinguish whether a response meets or falls short of this standard  Keep the ideal in mind as you design and refine your rubric — it’s what the model is aiming for\">"
