            {
              "id": "6e8c2a5f-9f04-4d00-8875-90ffdb41ba53",
              "weight": 0,
              "type": "rich_text",
              "contents": {
                "singleSelect": true,
                "body": "<img src=\"https://static.remotasks.com/uploads/6892e922522126f1742d8678/1754512955599_1qiyo.png\" alt=\"Key Problem Areas Hallucinations: Unsupported or inaccurate claims.  Irrelevant Additions: Unnecessary info not grounded in the prompt.  Formatting Issues: Inconsistent use of bullets, missing structure, or incorrect style.  Additional Mistakes Subtle Hallucinations: Small factual errors or exaggerations that sound believable.  Invalid Visual References: Assuming details in images are accurate without confirming.  Overlooking Format Cues: Missing embedded instructions in prompt wording.\">"
